Package tempest_foundation

Class DocumentGenerator

java.lang.Object
tempest_foundation.DocumentGenerator
public class DocumentGenerator extends Object
The DocumentGenerator class is responsible for generating PDF reports for student submissions. These reports include details such as the student's grade, the grade for individual methods, comments, and other relevant information about the student's submission.

This class includes methods for generating documents for successful submissions, failed submissions, or cases where no submission was made. It also supports creating overhead reports and appending data to them.

    • addOverheadData

      public static void addOverheadData(String formattedSeconds, String formattedMillis, String studentID, TestEnum testEnum) throws FileNotFoundException, com.itextpdf.text.DocumentException
      Adds data about the overhead time for a specific test and student to the overhead report.

      The method appends formatted information, including the test type, time in seconds and milliseconds, and the student ID, to the overhead report.

      Parameters:
      formattedSeconds - the formatted seconds of the overhead time.
      formattedMillis - the formatted milliseconds of the overhead time.
      studentID - the ID of the student associated with the overhead data.
      testEnum - the type of test for which the overhead data is being recorded.
      Throws:
      FileNotFoundException - if the overhead document's file cannot be found.
      com.itextpdf.text.DocumentException - if there is an error while writing to the overhead document.

    • addOverheadComment

      public static void addOverheadComment(String comment) throws FileNotFoundException, com.itextpdf.text.DocumentException
      Adds a custom comment to the overhead report.

      This method appends a provided comment to the overhead report as a new paragraph.

      Parameters:
      comment - the comment to add to the overhead report.
      Throws:
      FileNotFoundException - if the overhead document's file cannot be found.
      com.itextpdf.text.DocumentException - if there is an error while writing to the overhead document.

    • generateOverheadReport

      public static void generateOverheadReport()
      Finalizes and closes the overhead report.

      Once this method is called, no further data can be added to the overhead document. It ensures the document is properly saved and closed.
